window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>This revised and expanded edition of <i>The Essential Rumi</i> includes a new introduction by Coleman Barks and more than 80 never-before-published poems.</p> <p>Through his lyrical translations, Coleman Barks has been instrumental in bringing this exquisite literature to a remarkably wide range of listeners, making the ecstatic, spiritual poetry of 13th-century Sufi mystic Rumi more popular than ever.</p> <p><i>The Essential Rumi</i> continues to be the best-selling of all Rumi books and the definitive selection of his beautiful, mystical poetry.</p>"; 
